OL,6,FHer dad, Tim Edwards, set up the Elle
OL,7,FEdwards Foundation in her memory to
OL,8,Fhelp support other families who lose
OL,9,Floved ones to guns and violent crime.
OL,11,FIn March 2024, the foundation received
OL,12,Fofficial charity status, allowing it
OL,13,Fto help more people.
OL,15,FHe said: "The first thing we're gonna
OL,16,Fdo is start giving out scholarships
OL,17,Fand funding for women who want to
OL,18,Ffurther their careers.
OL,20,F"Especially in the beauty industry
OL,21,Fbecause it's relevant to Elle."
